      "amount": "1/2 tsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "Baking soda",
      "amount": "1/8 tsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "Plant-based milk or water",
      "amount": "150ml"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Blend tofu with flour, lemon juice, Dijon mustard, salt, lemon zest, garlic powder, red pepper flakes, and cumin in a food processor.",
    "Gradually add plant-based milk or water while blending until the mixture reaches a spreadable consistency.",
    "Heat olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat. Pour the tofu mixture into the pan and cook for 3-4 minutes on each side until golden brown.",
    "Sprinkle baking soda on top of the cooked wrap for an extra crisp texture, then return to the hot pan for another minute."
  ],
